00:15:17.330 --> 00:15:19.330
Što nakon toga?

00:15:19.330 --> 00:15:22.330
Hoćeš li preplivati Atlantik?

00:15:22.330 --> 00:15:24.330
Ne, ovo je posljednje.

00:15:24.330 --> 00:15:27.330
To je jedina plivačka dionica koja me zanima.

00:15:27.330 --> 00:15:29.330
Ali spremna sam.

00:15:29.330 --> 00:15:31.330
Inače, jedan me novinar nazvao neki dan

00:15:31.330 --> 00:15:33.330
i rekao je da je pogledao na Wikipediji

00:15:33.330 --> 00:15:36.330
i rekao da je vidio da sam se rodila 22. 8. 1949.

00:15:36.330 --> 00:15:38.330
i da zbog nekog čudnog razloga na Wikipediji

00:15:38.330 --> 00:15:40.330
imaju i datum moje smrti.

00:15:40.330 --> 00:15:42.330
(smijeh)

00:15:42.330 --> 00:15:45.330
Rekao je: "Jesi li znala da ćeš umrijeti na istom mjestu gdje si se rodila, u New Yorku,

00:15:45.330 --> 00:15:48.330
i bit će to biti u siječnju 2035.?"

00:15:48.330 --> 00:15:50.330
Rekoh: "Ne, nisam znala."

00:15:50.330 --> 00:15:52.330
Sad ću živjeti do 85. godine.

00:15:52.330 --> 00:15:55.330
Imam tri godine više nego što sam mislila.

00:15:56.330 --> 00:15:58.330
I pitam se,

00:15:58.330 --> 00:16:00.330
sada se počinjem pitati,

00:16:00.330 --> 00:16:02.330
čak i prije nego što ostvarim

00:16:02.330 --> 00:16:04.330
ovaj ekstreman san,

00:16:04.330 --> 00:16:06.330
pitam se,

00:16:06.330 --> 00:16:08.330
i možda bih to mogla upitati i vas večeras,

00:16:08.330 --> 00:16:13.330
da parafraziram pjesnikinju

00:16:13.330 --> 00:16:16.330
Mary Oliver,

00:16:16.330 --> 00:16:20.330
koja kaže: "Pa što je to,

00:16:20.330 --> 00:16:23.330
što to točno radiš

00:16:23.330 --> 00:16:28.330
s tim svojim divljim i dragocjenim životom?"

00:16:29.330 --> 00:16:31.330
Najljepša vam hvala.

